HOUSE RESOLUTION NO. 336
BY REPRESENTATIVE BAYHAM
COMMENDATIONS: Commends the valedictorians of the Holy Cross School 2026
graduating class
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To commend the valedictorians of the Holy Cross School 2026 graduating class.
3 WHEREAS, it is with great pride that the House of Representatives of the
4 Legislature of Louisiana recognizes individuals who contribute to the academic excellence
5 of the state; and
6 WHEREAS, Jacob William Guichard and Peter Jeffries Schissel are the
7 valedictorians of the graduating class of 2026 at Holy Cross School in New Orleans,
8 Louisiana; and
9 WHEREAS, founded in 1849, the Holy Cross School serves grades pre-kindergarten
10 through twelve; the school upholds a tradition of academic excellence with a focus on
11 developing boys of strong character and citizenship; and
12 WHEREAS, among the 2026 graduating class, Jacob and Peter are the highest-
13 performing students graduating from the distinguished school; both young men are deserving
14 of recognition for their outstanding achievements.
15 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
16 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Jacob William Guichard and Peter Jeffries
17 Schissel for graduating as the valedictorians of the Holy Cross School class of 2026 and does
18 hereby encourage them to continue their excellent work and always strive for greatness in
19 their scholastic endeavors.
